  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(* ===== Transfer-matrix machinery, ported verbatim from su2_XXX_L2.wb (cells 2-10) =====\n   Single-site GT-pattern generator machinery (ps,dim,J0,Jp,Jm,JJ), spin-s generators Ee and Lax\n   matrix L (uses global h), the shared companion twist G (set NUMERIC here with this file's κ1,κ2\n   so its eigenvalues are exactly κ1,κ2), the two-site embeddings L1/L2 (use global θ1,θ2), the\n   monodromy T, and the fundamental transfer matrix t2. *)\nClearAll[ps, dim, J0, Jp, Jm, JJ, Ee, L, L1, L2, T, t2, χ1, χ2, G];\nps[rep_] := ps[rep] = Block[{res = (Prepend[rep, #] & /@ (Tuples[Table[Range[rep[[1, i + 1]], rep[[1, i]]], {i, 1, Length[rep[[1]]] - 1}]]))}, If[Length[res[[1, 1]]] == 1, Reverse@Sort@res, Reverse@Sort@Flatten[ps /@ res, 1]]];\ndim[rep_] := dim[rep] = Length[ps[{rep}]];\nJ0[k_][pat_] := J0[k][pat] = Sum[pat[[k, i]], {i, 1, k}] - Sum[pat[[k - 1, i]], {i, 1, k - 1}];\nJp[k_][pat_] := Jp[k][pat] = -Sum[Product[pat[[k, i]] - i - pat[[k + 1, j]] + j, {j, Range[k + 1]}]/Product[pat[[k, i]] - i - pat[[k, j]] + j, {j, Complement[Range[k], {i}]}] v[ReplacePart[pat, {k, i} -> pat[[k, i]] + 1]], {i, 1, k}];\nJm[k_][pat_] := Jm[k][pat] = Sum[Product[pat[[k, i]] - i - pat[[k - 1, j]] + j, {j, Range[k - 1]}]/Product[pat[[k, i]] - i - pat[[k, j]] + j, {j, Complement[Range[k], {i}]}] v[ReplacePart[pat, {k, i} -> pat[[k, i]] - 1]], {i, 1, k}];\nJJ[k_, l_, rep_] := JJ[k, l, rep] = Which[k == l, DiagonalMatrix[J0[k] /@ ps[{rep}]], l == k + 1, Transpose[Table[Coefficient[Jp[k][ps[{rep}][[i]]], v[#]] & /@ ps[{rep}], {i, 1, Length[ps[{rep}]]}]], l == k - 1, Transpose[Table[Coefficient[Jm[l][ps[{rep}][[i]]], v[#]] & /@ ps[{rep}], {i, 1, Length[ps[{rep}]]}]], l > k + 1, JJ[k, k + 1, rep] . JJ[k + 1, l, rep] - JJ[k + 1, l, rep] . JJ[k, k + 1, rep], l < k - 1, JJ[k, k - 1, rep] . JJ[k - 1, l, rep] - JJ[k - 1, l, rep] . JJ[k, k - 1, rep]];\nEe[λ_][i_, j_] := JJ[i, j, {λ, 0}];\nL[λ_][i_, j_][u_] := KroneckerDelta[i, j]*u*IdentityMatrix[dim[{λ, 0}]] - h Ee[λ][j, i];\nχ1 = κ1 + κ2; χ2 = 1;\nG = {{χ1, -χ2}, {1, 0}};\nL1[λ1_, λ2_][i_, j_][u_] := KroneckerProduct[L[λ1][i, j][u - θ1], IdentityMatrix[dim[{λ2, 0}]]];\nL2[λ1_, λ2_][i_, j_][u_] := KroneckerProduct[IdentityMatrix[dim[{λ1, 0}]], L[λ2][i, j][u - θ2]];\nT[λ1_, λ2_][i_, j_][u_] := T[λ1, λ2][i, j][u] = Sum[L1[λ1, λ2][i, k][u] . L2[λ1, λ2][k, j][u], {k, 2}];\nt2[λ1_, λ2_][1, 1][u_] := Sum[T[λ1, λ2][i, j][u] G[[j, i]], {i, 2}, {j, 2}];\n(* sanity: char. poly of G is λ²-χ1 λ+χ2 = (λ-κ1)(λ-κ2), so {tr,det}(G) must equal {κ1+κ2,κ1 κ2}.\n   (NOT checked via Sort[Eigenvalues[G]]-Sort[{κ1,κ2}]: since κ2=Conjugate[κ1] exactly (|κ1|=1),\n   Eigenvalues[N[G]] introduces ~1e-17 real-part noise between the conjugate pair, which is enough\n   to flip Sort's ordering relative to the exact {κ1,κ2} and make an otherwise-correct check falsely\n   report an O(1) discrepancy. tr/det is the order-independent, numerically robust check.) *)\n{\"{tr,det}(G) - {κ1+κ2,κ1 κ2}\" -> Chop[{Tr[N[G]], Det[N[G]]} - {κ1 + κ2, κ1 κ2}], \"dim t2[1,1]\" -> Dimensions[t2[1, 1][1, 1][3]]}",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wl-output-block\"><div class=\"wl-output-header\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;width:100%;min-height:22px;\" data-session-epoch=\"598682\" data-output-id=\"20\" data-out-n=\"32\" data-sub-idx=\"17\" data-output-format=\"WLLatex\" data-output-is-graphics=\"0\" data-cell-idx=\"5\" data-sub-start=\"25\" data-sub-end=\"25\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-right:8px;\">Out[32]=</span></div><div class=\"wl-output-content\"><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrlwt03n-fc9pqqm\" data-page-width-em=\"14\" data-latex-b64=\"XGxlZnRce1x0ZXh0e1x7dHIsZGV0XH0oRykgLSBceyRca2FwcGEkMSskXGthcHBhJDIsJFxrYXBwYSQxICRca2FwcGEkMlx9fVx0byBcbGVmdFx7MCwwXHJpZ2h0XH0sXHRleHR7ZGltIHQyWzEsMV19XHRvIFxsZWZ0XHs0LDRccmlnaHRcfVxyaWdodFx9\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">{</span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">{tr,det}(G) - {</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">κ</span><span class=\"mord\">1+</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">κ</span><span class=\"mord\">2,</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">κ</span><span class=\"mord\">1 </span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">κ</span><span class=\"mord\">2}</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">→</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">{</span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">}</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">dim t2[1,1]</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">→</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">{</span><span class=\"mord\">4</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">4</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">}</span></span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\">}</span></span></span></span></span></span></div></div></div></div>",
       "mime": "x-application/wolfram-language-html"
      },
      {
       "data": "Out[32]= \\left\\{\\text{\\{tr,det\\}(G) - \\{$\\kappa$1+$\\kappa$2,$\\kappa$1 $\\kappa$2\\}}\\to \\left\\{0,0\\right\\},\\text{dim t2[1,1]}\\to \\left\\{4,4\\right\\}\\right\\}",
       "mime": "text/plain"
      }
     ],
     "id": "4deff48a-7b80-44b4-9b14-7c58cd0141cf"
    }
   ],
   "metadata": {}
  },
  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(* Coefficient matrices C0,C1,C2 with t2[λ1,λ2][1,1][u] = C0 + C1 u + C2 u^2.\n   Extracted entrywise via CoefficientList in a dummy variable (NOT by evaluating at numeric\n   points). Memoized per (λ1,λ2) — reusable across all (M,n) of that representation. *)\nClearAll[t2Coeffs];\nt2Coeffs[λ1_, λ2_] := t2Coeffs[λ1, λ2] = Module[{uu, mat, cl},\n   mat = t2[λ1, λ2][1, 1][uu];\n   cl = Map[PadRight[CoefficientList[#, uu], 3] &, mat, {2}];\n   Table[cl[[All, All, k]], {k, 1, 3}]\n];\n(* check: C2 must equal (κ1+κ2) Id — leading-order asymptotics match τ by construction *)\nWith[{Cs = t2Coeffs[1, 1]}, \"max|C2-(κ1+κ2)Id|\" -> Max[Abs[Flatten[Cs[[3]] - (κ1 + κ2) IdentityMatrix[4]]]]]",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wl-output-block\"><div class=\"wl-output-header\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;width:100%;min-height:22px;\" data-session-epoch=\"598682\" data-output-id=\"21\" data-out-n=\"35\" data-sub-idx=\"4\" data-output-format=\"WLLatex\" data-output-is-graphics=\"0\" data-cell-idx=\"6\" data-sub-start=\"10\" data-sub-end=\"10\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-right:8px;\">Out[35]=</span></div><div class=\"wl-output-content\"><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrlwt0hf-0t2i1h4\" data-page-width-em=\"14\" data-latex-b64=\"XHRleHR7bWF4fEMyLSgkXGthcHBhJDErJFxrYXBwYSQyKUlkfH1cdG8gMC5cdGltZXMgMTBeey0yOX0=\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord text\"><span class=\"mord\">max|C2-(</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">κ</span><span class=\"mord\">1+</span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\">κ</span><span class=\"mord\">2)Id|</span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span><span class=\"mrel\">→</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2778em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.7278em;vertical-align:-0.0833em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0.</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">×</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span></span><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:0.8641em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8641em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.113em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">−</span><span class=\"mord mtight\">29</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></div></div></div></div>",
       "mime": "x-application/wolfram-language-html"
      },
      {
       "data": "Out[35]= \\text{max|C2-($\\kappa$1+$\\kappa$2)Id|}\\to 0.\\times 10^{-29}",
       "mime": "text/plain"
