  {
   "kind": 2,
   "value": "(* Q1[λ1,λ2][M,n][u] = κ1^(u/h) q_n(u): the actual Baxter Q-function value, built from the SAME\n   QSolve cache (mutually consistent with τ by construction, since both trace back to the same\n   TauEigensystem[λ1,λ2][{M,n}] entry). *)\nClearAll[Q1];\nQ1[λ1_, λ2_][M_, n_][u_] := Module[{q = QSolve[λ1, λ2][M, n]},\n  If[q === $Failed, $Failed, κ1^(u/h) qpoly[q, u]]];\n(* smoke test *)\n{Q1[1, 1][1, 0][2], N[τ[1, 1][1, 0][2], 10]}",
   "languageId": "wolfram",
   "outputs": [
    {
     "items": [
      {
       "data": "<div class=\"wl-output-block\"><div class=\"wl-output-header\" style=\"display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;width:100%;min-height:22px;\" data-session-epoch=\"598682\" data-output-id=\"28\" data-out-n=\"76\" data-sub-idx=\"4\" data-output-format=\"WLLatex\" data-output-is-graphics=\"0\" data-cell-idx=\"13\" data-sub-start=\"7\" data-sub-end=\"7\"><span style=\"font-size:10px;color:#888;margin-right:8px;\">Out[76]=</span></div><div class=\"wl-output-content\"><div class=\"vscode-wolfram-wllatex-prerendered wl-lb-pending\" data-lb-id=\"lb-mrlwtey3-jty6ruk\" data-page-width-em=\"14\" data-latex-b64=\"XGxlZnRcey0wLjcwOTIzMTAxMDk1ODAxNjkyNjUzNzIyNTE0MisxLjA5NTk2OTE2MjUxMjc3MjA2NzA2NzUyNzI4XCxcbWF0aHJte2l9LC0wLjAyMjkxNjYwOTAwKzAuXHRpbWVzIDEwXnstMTJ9XCxcbWF0aHJte2l9XHJpZ2h0XH0=\" style=\"opacity:0.65;transition:opacity 0.35s\"><div class=\"wl-lb-content\"><span class=\"katex-display\"><span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1.2141em;vertical-align:-0.35em;\"></span><span class=\"minner\"><span class=\"mopen delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\"><span class=\"delimsizing size1\">{</span></span><span class=\"mord\">−</span><span class=\"mord\">0.709231010958016926537225142</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1.09596916251277206706752728</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathrm\">i</span><span class=\"mpunct\">,</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">−</span><span class=\"mord\">0.02291660900</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">+</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">0.</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mbin\">×</span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.2222em;\"></span><span class=\"mord\">1</span><span class=\"mord\"><span class=\"mord\">0</span><span class=\"msupsub\"><span class=\"vlist-t\"><span class=\"vlist-r\"><span class=\"vlist\" style=\"height:0.8641em;\"><span style=\"top:-3.113em;margin-right:0.05em;\"><span class=\"pstrut\" style=\"height:2.7em;\"></span><span class=\"sizing reset-size6 size3 mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\"><span class=\"mord mtight\">−</span><span class=\"mord mtight\">12</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class=\"mspace\" style=\"margin-right:0.1667em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathrm\">i</span><span class=\"mclose delimcenter\" style=\"top:0em;\"><span class=\"delimsizing size1\">}</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></div></div></div></div>",
       "mime": "x-application/wolfram-language-html"
